     1‚Üí# humanize
    12‚ÜíThis modest package contains various common humanization utilities, like turning a
    13‚Üínumber into a fuzzy human-readable duration ("3 minutes ago") or into a human-readable
    14‚Üísize or throughput. It is localized to:
    15‚Üí
    16‚Üí- Arabic
    17‚Üí- Basque
    18‚Üí- Bengali
    19‚Üí- Brazilian Portuguese
    20‚Üí- Catalan
    21‚Üí- Danish
    22‚Üí- Dutch
    23‚Üí- Esperanto
    24‚Üí- European Portuguese
    25‚Üí- Finnish
    26‚Üí- French
    27‚Üí- German
    28‚Üí- Greek
    29‚Üí- Hebrew
    30‚Üí- Indonesian
    31‚Üí- Italian
    32‚Üí- Japanese
    33‚Üí- Klingon
